=== impersonating ===
Vampire: I’m looking for a suspect named Seymour Orion in this crime. 
Villager: Umm, I don’t know anybody named Seymour Orion… What did he do?
Vampire: I’m going to need to search your house to find him. We have a warrant. Can I come in? 
{~He shows a fake warrant.|He shows a real warrant.}

Villager: {~Oh. Okay. Fine, you can come in.|I don’t know. I still don’t want you coming inside.}

{~Vampire barges into the house.|Vampire decides to leave.}
    -> END

